snippet.title: Finding Nemo: The Video Game - Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
A full, start-to-finish playthrough of the Finding Nemo video game that was released in 2003 for the Sony PlayStation 2, Nintendo GameCube, and Microsoft Xbox. For some timestamps, click on "SHOW MORE".

Timestamps:

2:14 - Level 1: Going to School
7:18 - Level 2: Field Trip
13:23 - Level 3:  The Drop Off
18:04 - Level 4: Mask Chase
23:08 - Level 5: Catch Dory
27:41 - Level 6: Minefield
34:30 - Level 7: Submarine
44:47 - Level 8: Hide and Seek
49:13 - Level 9: Mask Search
59:44 - Level 10: Anglerfish Chase
1:02:06 - Level 11: Mount Wannahockaloogie
1:05:54 - Level 12: Jellyfish Race
1:13:23 - Level 13: Training with Gill
1:19:30 - Level 14: East Australian Current
1:22:57 - Level 15: The Plan
1:30:32 - Level 16: Whale Chase
1:35:32 - Level 17: Treatment Plant
1:41:49 - Level 18: Fishing Net Rescue

Notes:

-Captured from real hardware, not an Emulator
-Played using a regular controller
-No cheats used
-Movie cutscenes edited out

Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Mega_Man_52

#FindingNemo #Pixar #TravelersTales
